{
  "texts": [
    "The first convolutional layer consists of 32 filters, each of size 3 × 3.",
    "These filters are adept at recognizing intricate patterns and structures within the images.",
    "The rectified linear unit (ReLU) activation function is applied to introduce nonlinearity, enabling the network to capture complex relationships in the data.",
    "Max pooling layers are interspersed between the convolutional layers.",
    "These layers serve to reduce the spatial dimensions of the data while retaining the most salient features."
  ]
}